snippet.title: FictionSphere Gameplay Mechanics
snippet.description:
Hey All We're just about ready to hold a demo test, so we wanted you guys to get familiarized with the different mechanics coming to the test! As promised the previous backers will have a shot at it first while everyone else will get a chance later on!
